contents.description: Churails is an Urdu language ZEE5 Exclusive Zindagi Original series starring Sarwat Gilani, Mehar Bano, Nirma Bucha, and Yasra Rizvi. Set in Karachi, the series revolves around four young women who form a secret detective agency under the guise of a fashion store named Halal Designs with the purpose of finding and exposing unfaithful husbands amongst Karachis elite.
contents.title: Churails

contents.description: Date with Saie is a ZEE5 Original starring Sai Tamhankar as herself. The story revolves around a popular actress who is stalked by a fan, who places cameras to track her moves and make a film on her life. What happens when Saie finds out about the cameras and the crazy fan posing a threat to her private life?
contents.title: Date With Saie

contents.description: A couple suffers a setback when the groom realises that he suffers from erectile dysfunction. How will it impact their wedding celebrations and marriage plan?
contents.title: Shubh Mangal Saavdhan

contents.description: The movie revolves around the surgical strike executed by the Indian Army on suspected militants who attacked an army base in Uri, Jammu and Kashmir, in 2016.
contents.title: Uri: The Surgical Strike

contents.description: Simmba enjoys being an immoral and unethical police officer until a life-changing event transforms him and forces him to choose the righteous path.
contents.title: Simmba

contents.description: Murad and his daughter-in-law set out to fight a legal battle to prove their innocence after their family gets accused of having ties with extremist groups.
contents.title: Mulk

contents.description: Four childhood friends, who are now fierce and independent women, reunite for a bachelorette trip that’ll help them rediscover themselves.
contents.title: Veere Di Wedding

contents.description: Rockstar is a 2011 romantic drama starring Ranbir Kapoor, Nargis Fakhri, Aditi Rao Hydari, Kumud Mishra, Piyush Mishra and Shammi Kapoor. Janardhan aspires to be a Rockstar and believes that pain and suffering gets the best out of an artist. In order to get his heart broken, he proposes Heer, the most beautiful girl in Delhi University.
contents.title: Rockstar

contents.description: Bitti falls in love with an author and tries to reach him through Chirag. Hilarity ensues when Chirag himself falls for Bitti and tries to impress her.
contents.title: Bareilly Ki Barfi

contents.description: Tamasha is a 2015 Hindi romantic drama film starring Ranbir Kapoor and Deepika Padukone. Irshad Kamil won the Filmfare Award for Best Lyricist for this film.The story revolves around Ved who meets Tara during a holiday to Corsica. Tara gets quite impressed with Ved’s excitement and cheerful nature. However, when they meet in India, Tara finds Ved to be a completely opposite. Is Ved hiding his emotions and true personality? Will Tara find the real Dev that she loves?
contents.title: Tamasha

contents.description: Haider is a 2014 Hindi crime drama starring Shahid Kapoor, Tabu, Shraddha Kapoor and Kay Kay Menon. Haider, a young man, returns to Jammu and Kashmir after finishing his education. Haider tries to get closure regarding his father's sudden disappearance after a military raid on his house. He is disturbed seeing his mother's closeness with his uncle, Khurram. Will Haider be able to avenge his father's death?
contents.title: Haider

contents.description: Wanted is a 2009 Hindi action film starring Salman Khan, Ayesha Takia and Prakash raj. The movie was one of the highest grossing films of the year and was lauded for its action. Wanted revolves around Radhe, a ruthless gangster who kills people for money. Radhe falls in love with Jhanvi but doesn’t commit due to his dangerous profession. When international don Ghani Bhai lands in India, an undercover cop is assigned the task to arrest him. Will the don ever be nabbed?
contents.title: Wanted

contents.description: Ghajini is a 2008 Hindi action thriller film starring Aamir Khan, Asin, Jiah Khan and Pradeep Rawat. Sanjay Singhania, a prominent businessman, falls in love with Kalpana, who is a model. A cruel twist of fate separates the two lovers when Ghajini, a ruthless criminal, enters their life.
contents.title: Ghajini

contents.description:
Partner is a 2007 romantic film starring Govinda,  Salman Khan,  Katrina Kaif,  Lara Dutta and others. The film is based on Will Smith's Hitch. 

A nerdy under-confident man is in love with his stunning boss. He takes the help of a dating and love guru,  Prem to win her over. Prem himself is in love with a woman. What follows is a sequence of funny events during which the boss also falls in love with the man. But she has to marry someone of her father's choice. What will the man and his love guru do now?
contents.title: Partner

contents.description: Cheeni Kum is a 2007 Bollywood romance film directed by R. Balki and starring Amitabh Bachchan, Tabu, Paresh Rawal, Zohra Sehgal and Swini Khara. The story is about After an initial disagreement about the quality of his food, London restaurateur Buddhadev Gupta (Amitabh Bachchan) and diner Nina Verma (Tabu) hit it off. Though he's in his 60s and she's in her 30s, they're soon engaged. When Nina returns to India to assist her ailing father (Paresh Rawal), Buddhadev follows in the hope of impressing her family. But, like Buddhadev's mother (Zohra Sehgal), the elder Verma objects to the relationship, leaving the lovers in a tough situation..
contents.title: Cheeni Kum

contents.description: Gadar: Ek Prem Katha is a 2001 Hindi action drama film featuring Sunny Deol, Amisha Patel and Amrish Puri. The story revolves around the partition of India. Tara Singh falls in love with a muslim girl, saves her life from fellow Sikhs and eventually, marries her. They live happily until Sakina's father enters their life and hatches a plan to separate the two. Sakina moves to Pakistan while Tara struggles to reunite with his love.
contents.title: Gadar: Ek Prem Katha

contents.description: Kaho Naa... Pyaar Hai is a 2000 romantic thriller starring Hrithik Roshan and Ameesha Patel in the lead roles. Rohit and Sonia are madly in love, but Rohit’s mysterious death shatters Sonia. To overcome the pain of loss, she travels to New Zealand, where she meets Rohit’s lookalike Raj.
contents.title: Kaho Naa... Pyaar Hai

contents.description: Karan Arjun is a 1995 action drama starring Salman Khan, Shah Rukh Khan, Rakhee Gulzar, Kajol, Mamta Kulkarni, and Amrish Puri. Thakur Durjan Singh, the evil uncle of Karan and Arjun, gets them brutally murdered. Years later, the brothers are reincarnated and return to avenge their death.
contents.title: Karan Arjun

contents.description: Mohra is a 1994 action thriller movie starring Akshay Kumar, Suniel Shetty, Raveena Tandon, Naseeruddin Shah and Paresh Rawal. Vishal, a prisoner, is released from the jail and hired by Mr Jindal to eliminate criminals of two rival gangs. Vishal starts killing the criminals one by one until Amar, an honest police officer, comes in his way. Will Vishal and Amar ever find out who the real enemy is?
contents.title: Mohra

contents.description: Qayamat Se Qayamat Tak is a 1988 Hindi drama film starring Aamir Khan, Juhi Chawla, Dalip Tahil, Alok Nath. Raj and Rashmi belong to two rival families. The duo falls in love and decides to get married despite severe opposition from their families. With their families trying to separate them, will their love stand the test of time?
contents.title: Qayamat Se Qayamat Tak

contents.description: Don, a gangster, dies during a police chase. Vijay, Don's lookalike, infiltrates his gang on DSP D'Silva's orders to gather information but a change of events lands him in trouble.
contents.title: Don

contents.description: In this ZEE5 Original film, a transgender, Haddi moves to Delhi and joins a gang of transgenders and cross-dressers headed by an influential man. But is this move aspirational or driven by revenge?
contents.title: Haddi

contents.description: This ZEE5 Original film follows the journey of India's iconic home chef, Tarla Dalal. It captures the integral role she played in empowering women and helping them realise their dreams through food.
contents.title: Tarla

contents.description: While one agent is out to rescue Dr. Tailor from abductors, another agent is trying to find the cause of a Zombie Attack on San Francisco. All clues lead them to a bizarre island. What horrors follow?
contents.title: Resident Evil: Death Island

contents.description: An introverted teenager, Ruby is shocked when she accidentally discovers her true lineage that connects her to the mythical sea Kraken. How will she come to terms with her new reality?
contents.title: Ruby Gillman, Teenage Kraken

contents.description: In the 1800s in colonial-era Punjab, Jeona Maurh takes up arms to avenge his bandit brother's death. He gradually takes on the land tax mafia working in cahoots with the native kings and the British.
contents.title: Maurh

contents.description: In this ZEE5 Original film, Radhika, a journalism intern's investigation into bike riders violating traffic on a city flyover, turns sinister when she becomes a suspect in the murder of a motorist.
contents.title: U-Turn

contents.description: Bhaijaan, a self-avowed bachelor, decides to give up on violence when he falls in love with Bhagyalakshmi. Will he go back to his old ways when he learns about her family's rivalry with a gangster?
contents.title: Kisi Ka Bhai Kisi Ki Jaan

contents.description: In this ZEE5 Original film, an ace undercover agent living as a housewife is assigned a task after a decade. How will she accomplish her mission of finding a serial killer with her forgotten skills?
contents.title: Mrs Undercover

contents.description: Jamnaprasad, a renowned miser, secretly saves all his money to fulfil his father's wish to go on the Char Dham Yatra. Hell breaks loose when his parents go missing during the tour due to heavy floods.
contents.title: Kanjoos Makhichoos

contents.description: This ZEE5 Original narrates the tale of crime reporter Vidhi, who is out to find a missing college student. Her quest reveals the many layers of society that redefine politics, love, and betrayal.
contents.title: Lost

contents.description: Police informer Ghulam holds the force responsible when his brother gets killed in a gang war. As he then kick-starts his own business, he wrongfully gets involved in a series of bomb attacks.
contents.title: Operation Fryday

contents.description: This ZEE5 Original movie revolves around Sanya, a chemistry genius who decides to use her skills to educate the youth on safe sex and bring about a much-needed social change while looking for a job.
contents.title: Chhatriwali

contents.description: Arjun Bakshi, an animal lover, discovers an illegal animal trade cell in Kolkata. He turns into a vigilante to save the animals and chances upon a rare species of the Indian black-striped hyena.
contents.title: Lakadbaggha

contents.description: An investigative journalist finds a fake account of her niece on social media. Her trail of investigation leads her to Aalim, a Libyan man wanted by the FBI. What happens next?
contents.title: Raangi

contents.description: A once peaceful man, Vedha, goes on a revenge killing spree with his daughter, Kanaka, after she gets released from prison. A daunting inspector Ramaa tries to stop the duo, only to be outrun by them.
contents.title: Vedha

contents.description: Anand and Swamy are lookalikes. One is the CEO of an enterprise, and the other is a street-smart unemployed man. Chaos ensues when both of them fall in love with the same girl, Pranavi.
contents.title: Big Dhamaka

contents.description: Natasha is married to Rohan, who plans to kill her for her inheritance. What happens when he is the one who's found dead? Will investigating officer Mohan Khanna be able to solve the mystery?
contents.title: Shadyantra

contents.description: In this ZEE5 Original, Gayatri, a woman with a degenerative eye disorder, is slowly losing her eyesight. She, however, has to solve the mystery of her twin sister Gautami's death. This audio version of the film has been specially created for the visually impaired.
contents.title: Blurr - Audio Description Version

contents.description: In this ZEE5 Original, Gayatri, a woman with a degenerative eye disorder, is slowly losing her eyesight. She, however, has to solve the mystery of her twin sister Gautami's death.
contents.title: Blurr

contents.description: This ZEE5 Original film follows the stories of four individuals from different strata of society during the 21-day lockdown imposed by the Indian government in the wake of the COVID-19 pandemic.
contents.title: India Lockdown

contents.description: Araka, a cruel drug baron, kidnaps innocent villagers and forces them to work for him. But, when Bhajarangi, a forest officer, learns about this, he decides to come to the villagers' rescue.
contents.title: Bhajarangi 2

contents.description: Shahjahan is a skilled locksmith who leads an honest life. But he finds himself in a precarious situation when he is forced to join hands with a bunch of policemen involved in a robbery.
contents.title: Puksatte Lifu

contents.description: A barber’s decision to take revenge on his ex-girlfriend turns adventurous after he realises that her husband is a notorious gangster.
contents.title: Hero

contents.description: A common man's police complaint about his missing shadow prompts the police to reopen the case of a road accident that might have been a murder.
contents.title: Shadow

contents.description: Ram, an insurance agent, cares about the people who live in his locality and decides to fight for them when a medical scam puts their lives at risk.
contents.title: Ramarjuna

contents.description: Shivaji Surathkal is a 2020 Kannada mystery thriller movie, starring Ramesh Aravind and Radhika Narayan. The story revolves around Shivaji Surathkal, a cop, who arrives at a private resort in Ranagiri to investigate the suspicious murder of Roshan, the state Home Minister's son. The situation, however, turns complex when Shivaji, who is already haunted by his wife's unexpected death, begins experiencing spooky incidents.
contents.title: Shivaji Surathkal

contents.description: Popcorn Monkey Tiger is a 2020 Kannada crime drama movie starring Dhananjay and Niveditha. The story revolves around Tiger Seena, a mechanic, who falls in love with Popcorn Devi, a popcorn seller. Things take an unexpected turn after Seena becomes a gangster, only to find Popcorn Devi already involved with the underworld changing their lives forever.
contents.title: Popcorn Monkey Tiger (a)

contents.description: Kalidasa Kannada Meshtru is a 2019 Kannada comedy-drama movie starring Jaggesh and Meghana Gaonkar in the lead roles. Kalidasa, a teacher at a Kannada medium school, decides to fight against the education system and society, which favour privatised English medium schools when his school faces the threat of a shutdown.
contents.title: Kalidasa Kannada Meshtru

contents.description: Panchatantra is a 2019 Kannada romantic drama movie starring Vihan Gowda, Akshara Gowda and Sonal Monteiro. The story revolves around a bunch of youngsters and senior citizens who decide to compete against each other in a car rally, to own a piece of land that's under litigation. Who will win the car rally and take control of the land?
contents.title: Panchatantra

contents.description: When Nischay, a NRI businessman, discovers that he was adopted by the couple he considers his parents 25 years ago, he decides to return to India in search of his biological parents. Will he succeed?
contents.title: Missing Boy

contents.description: Seetharama Kalyana is a 2019 Kannada romantic action movie starring Nikhil Kumaraswamy and Rachita Ram.
contents.title: Seetharama Kalyana

contents.description: The Villain is a 2018 Kannada action drama movie starring Sudeep, Shiva Rajkumar, Amy Jackson and others. The story revolves between Ram and Raavan, who battle against each other, portraying the 'good' and 'bad' on this world that lie within ourselves. Is Shiva Rajkumar the Raavan or is it Sudeep? Who wins the final battle? Is it Ram's ideology that works or is it Ravana's brilliance that lasts?
contents.title: The Villain

contents.description: Rajaratha is a 2018 Kannada romantic comedy film starring Nirup Bhandari, Avantika Shetty and Shruthi Hariharan. The movie is based on 2 simultaneously-running stories -  The 1st story revolves around Abhi and Megha who are travelling in a bus named 'Rajaratha' to Chennai, while the 2nd story revolves around Vishwa who works in-hand with the current political ruling party. How these two separate characters and stories are combined together makes the movie all the more interesting.
contents.title: Rajaratha

contents.description: Hebbuli is a 2017 Kannada action thriller film starring Sudeep, V. Ravichandran and Amala Paul. The story revolves around Captain Ram, a Para Commando Officer, who sets out to find the culprits and motive behind his brother’s death. His search leads him to fight the system and pursue to fulfil his brother’s vision.
contents.title: Hebbuli

contents.description: Doddmane Hudga is a 2016 Kannada action drama film starring Puneeth Rajkumar, Radhika Pandit and Ambareesh.The story revolves around Surya, son of a respected family, who leaves home due to his troubled relation with his father Rajivappa. However, he returns after a few years, to rescue his land from Babu, an evil man.
contents.title: Doddmane Hudga

contents.description:
Bhajarangi is a 2013 Kannada adventure film starring Shivrajkumar, Aindrita Ray, and Madhu Guruswamy. 
A cruel Tantrik harasses the people of Ramadurga. When Jeevan, comes to the village to learn about his ancestors, he ends up bravely opposes him and fights to save the villagers.
contents.title: Bhajarangi

contents.description: In a joint family, Arjan Singh, a dominating son-in-law, begins to lose his importance with the arrival of a new adorable son-in-law. What ensues is a hilarious tale of rivalry between the two.
contents.title: Fuffad Ji

contents.description: Desperate to make some quick money, Lucky and his friends rob an e-commerce company truck. But to their surprise, the looted boxes contain condoms instead of electronic gadgets. What will Lucky do?
contents.title: Helmet

contents.description: Comedy Couple is a ZEE5 Original film, starring Saqib Saleem, Shweta Basu Prasad, Pooja Bedi, and Aadar Malik. The movie revolves around the lives of Zoya and Deep–a stand-up comedy duo and real-life lovers. They are a laugh-riot on stage with their sharp and witty take on a variety of issues like relationship problems while grappling with them off-stage.
contents.title: Comedy Couple

contents.description: Happy Phirr Bhag Jayegi is a 2018 Hindi comedy starring Sonakshi Sinha, Jimmy Shergill, Jassie Gill, Diana Penty, Ali Fazal and Piyush Mishra. The movie is a sequel to the 2016 film Happy Bhag Jayegi. The second part showcases a comedy of errors that occurs when goons in China mistakenly kidnap a horticulture professor named Happy instead of her namesake who travelled by the same flight.
contents.title: Happy Phirr Bhag Jayegi

contents.description: Four childhood friends, who are now fierce and independent women, reunite for a bachelorette trip that’ll help them rediscover themselves.
contents.title: Veere Di Wedding

contents.description: Satyendra and Aarti meet for an arranged marriage and fall in love. Things go downhill when she runs away on their wedding day to pursue her career.
contents.title: Shaadi Mein Zaroor Aana

contents.description: Bitti falls in love with an author and tries to reach him through Chirag. Hilarity ensues when Chirag himself falls for Bitti and tries to impress her.
contents.title: Bareilly Ki Barfi

contents.description: Behen Hogi Teri is a 2017 Hindi romantic comedy film starring Rajkumar Rao, Shruti Haasan and Gautam Gulati. Gattu loves his neighbour Binny but the society expects all boys to treat the neighbouring girls as their sisters. When Binny’s parents seek a groom for her, Gattu is never considered which irks him. How will Gattu convince the parents and the society and win over Binny’s love.
contents.title: Behen Hogi Teri

contents.description: A Flying Jatt is a 2016 Hindi action adventure film starring Tiger Shroff and Jacqueline Fernandez. The story revolves around Aman, a meek youngster, who suddenly gains superpowers. Malhotra, an industrialist responsible for polluting the environment, wants to acquire a piece of land that belongs to Aman’s family. He ropes in Raka, a mutant, to cut a holy tree on the land, but Aman manages to stop Raka from felling the tree. With his superpower, can Aman stop Malhotra and Raka from further polluting the environment?
contents.title: A Flying Jatt

contents.description: Happy Bhag Jayegi is a 2016 romantic comedy, starring Diana Penty, Abhay Deol, Jimmy Shergill and Ali Fazal. On the day of her marriage to Bagga, a businessman, Harpreet Happy Kaur elopes with her boyfriend, Guddu. She ends up in a truck heading to Lahore where she meets Bilal, an upcoming politician. An angry Bagga abducts Guddu and reaches Lahore in search of Happy. What ensues is a hilarious cat and mouse chase.
contents.title: Happy Bhag Jayegi

contents.description: Entertainment is a 2014 Hindi comedy film starring Akshay Kumar and Tamannaah Bhatia. Writer duo Sajid-Farhad of Golmaal and Singham fame, make their directorial debut with this comic-caper. Entertainment is the story of Akhil, a struggler, who discovers that his biological father was a multi-millionaire and has just passed away.  When Akhil goes to claim his inheritance, he discovers that the wealth has been inherited by a dog named Entertainment. This light-hearted comedy explains why a dog is called man’s best friend.
contents.title: Entertainment

contents.description: Main Tera Hero is a 2014 Hindi romantic comedy starring Varun Dhawan, Nargis Fakhri and Ileana D’Cruz. Seenu is in love with Sunaina but has to fend off corrupt officer Angad, who too loves her. When things finally seem hunky-dory, Sunaina gets kidnapped. To save her, Seenu must marry Ayesha, the daughter of her kidnapper. Will Seenu’s love for Sunaina help him save her?
contents.title: Main Tera Hero

contents.description: Rascals is a 2011 comedy film starring Sanjay Dutt, Ajay Devgn, Kangana Ranaut and Arjun Rampal. Con artists, Chetan and Bhagat, fall in love with Khushi and try to woo her. However, Anthony, an old nemesis arrives and kidnaps Khushi to foil their plan.
contents.title: Rascals

contents.description: Dhamaal is a 2007 comedy movie starring Sanjay Dutt, Arshad Warsi, Riteish Deshmukh, Javed Jaffrey and Aashish Chaudhary. After finding about a hidden treasure from a dying man, four good-for-nothing friends embark on a race against time to find the treasure. However, their plans are foiled by Inspector Kabir who is hellbent to get the treasure all by himself.
contents.title: Dhamaal

contents.description:
Partner is a 2007 romantic film starring Govinda,  Salman Khan,  Katrina Kaif,  Lara Dutta and others. The film is based on Will Smith's Hitch. 

A nerdy under-confident man is in love with his stunning boss. He takes the help of a dating and love guru,  Prem to win her over. Prem himself is in love with a woman. What follows is a sequence of funny events during which the boss also falls in love with the man. But she has to marry someone of her father's choice. What will the man and his love guru do now?
contents.title: Partner

contents.description: The show essays the eternal bond shared by the little Shiva with his mother, Mahasati Anusuya, exploring an unheard and untold chapter of Lord Shivas life.
contents.title: Baal Shiv

contents.description: Krisha Chaturvedi’s life is no less than a fairy tale when she marries her love, Devraj. But Krisha soon finds herself in a swamp full of lies and deceit.
contents.title: Tere Bina Jiya Jaye Na

contents.description: Niyati, a nurse, feels inexplicably drawn towards a mentally ill patient named Aditya and decides to nurse him back to health. She soon learns that there is more to Aditya’s life than meets the eye.
contents.title: Aggar Tum Na Hote

contents.description: Diya, a gully badminton player, meets Arjun, a former badminton champ from an affluent family, who resents his own kin. Will Diya bring back the much-needed positivity and hope in Arujn’s life?
contents.title: Rishton Ka Manjha

contents.description: Lakshmi a kind hearted girl, hailing from a middle-class family, strongly believes in helping others, but her life takes an unexpected turn when her fate is tied to Rishi Oberoi, an industrialists son.
contents.title: Bhagya Lakshmi

contents.description: Protected and pampered as a child, Kashibai rises to the challenge and proves to be an able administrator when her husband Peshwa Bajirao sets out to expand the Maratha empire.
contents.title: Kashibai Bajirao Ballal

contents.description: Happu Singh, a family man, works hard as a police constable. However, all his efforts turn out to be futile as his life is constantly riddled with difficulties, often leading to a comedy of errors.
contents.title: Happu Ki Ultan Paltan

contents.description: Karan marries Preeta out of spite owing to a misunderstanding. Preeta tries to clear the air and wins him over whilst dealing with Sherlyn, Prithvi, and Mahira, a trio that becomes a thorn in her side.
contents.title: Kundali Bhagya
